The paper proposes a machine learning framework for improving the efficiency and safety of automated driving policies. The paper discusses various machine learning techniques such as optimal control, model-based solutions, model-free solutions, reinforcement learning, and imitation learning. The proposed framework is based on data set aggregation and meta-learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
